Yokai Heart							KEY:Chu Ye Enforcer ~ Yokai Heart													CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:VigilanteClassFeatures.ChuYeEnforcerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																															DESC:A Chu Ye enforcer seeks to transmute himself into a destructive spirit and terrorize his enemies. His vigilante identity alignment must be non-good. While in his vigilante identity, the Chu Ye enforcer gains darkvision with a range of 60 feet and low-light vision, and he counts as both a native outsider with the oni subtype and his original type for any effect related to type, whichever is worse for him.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										SOURCEPAGE:p.18
Oni Mask							KEY:Chu Ye Enforcer ~ Oni Mask														CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:VigilanteClassFeatures.ChuYeEnforcerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																															DESC:A Chu Ye enforcer gains a grotesque horned mask that he must wear when assuming his vigilante identity. The mask has %1 hit points and hardness 5. While wearing the mask, the Chu Ye enforcer gains a +%2 bonus to Intimidate. Without this mask, a Chu Ye enforcer can't assume his vigilante identity. A Chu Ye enforcer who loses his mask can replace it after 1 day through a specialized ritual that takes 8 hours to complete and costs 200 gp per vigilante level he has. This alters dual identity.|10*VigilanteLVL|max(1,VigilanteLVL/2)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.18
