Deceitful Form						KEY:Chu Ye Enforcer ~ Deceitful Form												CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:VigilanteClassFeatures.ChuYeEnforcerClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.SpellLike																																																																																																							DEFINE:ChuYeShapeTime|0				DESC:A Chu Ye enforcer gains the shapechanger subtype and the ability to change his form, as per Alter Self, for %1 minutes per day. These minutes do not need to be consecutive, but they must be spent in 1-minute increments.|ChuYeShapeTime|PREMULT:2,[PREVARGTEQ:VigilanteLVL,4],[PREVARLT:VigilanteLVL,14] 			DESC:A Chu Ye enforcer gains the shapechanger subtype and the ability to change his form, as per Giant Form I, for %1 minutes per day. These minutes do not need to be consecutive, but they must be spent in 1-minute increments.|ChuYeShapeTime|PREMULT:2,[PREVARGTEQ:VigilanteLVL,14],[PREVARLT:VigilanteLVL,18]		DESC:A Chu Ye enforcer gains the shapechanger subtype and the ability to change his form, as per Giant Form II, for %1 minutes per day. These minutes do not need to be consecutive, but they must be spent in 1-minute increments.|ChuYeShapeTime|PREVARGTEQ:VigilanteLVL,18																																																																																																												BONUS:VAR|ChuYeShapeTime|VigilanteLVL																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.18
